The paper discusses the use of chatbots to mediate task management for teams, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The focus on team collaboration and communication suggests the relevance of computer-supported cooperative work (cs.CSCW) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the use of bots to manage tasks may involve information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques to search and organize task-related information.
